data.description: This spacious 5-bedroom, 2-baths home is located in Wynchase Crossing.  The home offers an open floor plan with built in shelving and cabinets.  The kitchen has a nice size island and opens up directly to the dining area.  This home sits on 1.373 acres with a scenic view in the back.  With a little TLC this home could be a great place to raise a family.
